        <a href="" class="nav-link relative overflow-hidden flex md:text-[1.5em] lg:text-[13.5px] px-[16px] py-[10px] mr-3 justify-center items-center border border-[#fff] radius rounded-[40px] bg-white text-accent hover:bg-[#222] hover:text-primary transition duration-300">About</a>
